{"tid":1423112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華人真係一個好戇鳩既人種(包括香港人)","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T13:42:08.000Z","uid":83251,"like":219,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9559610f2fdce12239787584436ff8f96d202e24","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"華人真係一個好戇鳩既人種(包括香港人)<br />\n佢地只會一味崇拜權力同權威<br />\n權力同權威就好似佢地心中既神咁<br />\n一旦呢個神不存在或沒落時<br />\n佢地就會失去安全感,感到焦慮<br />\n所以你一搞事,佢地就會罵你<br />\n因為佢覺得你破壞左佢心中既神<br />\n如果有一日,呢D權力同權威沒落<br />\n佢地就會咸苦咸忽,似係世界末日咁<br />\n<br />\n你睇新加坡,新加坡比馬來西亞趕走時,成班好似痴左線咁就知<br />\n<br />\n現在共產黨執政,成班就覺得共產黨岩哂,共產黨最好<br />\n當共產黨玩完,比另一個新既黨管時<br />\n佢地就會全民屌共產黨,話新黨岩哂<br />\n毫無事非判斷能力<br />\n佢地既判斷就是,誰有權力同權威,就係岩哂<br />\n<br />\n智障民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47256d78c8aa60b9f9335d08265260c5a132555","tid":1423112,"uid":258258,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"totally agree <br />\n成日講咩環境唔變就人變<br />\n係要奴隸化<br />\n又鐘意blame the victim 真心on 9<br />\n試下去法國講呢D on 9 野實笑死人"},{"pid":"30c92dcde8bb77d6300f2ae5c449e8061f8d500b","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"a47256d78c8aa60b9f9335d08265260c5a132555","tid":1423112,"uid":258258,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"totally agree <br />\n成日講咩環境唔變就人變<br />\n係要奴隸化<br />\n又鐘意blame the victim 真心on 9<br />\n試下去法國講呢D on 9 野實笑死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"又話努力就有前途<br />\n係,努力係重要既<br />\n但係,佢地無諗過<br />\n努力有用只係個環境reward你既努力<br />\n如果個系統無reward你既努力既設定<br />\n你多多努力都無用,你跳十次樓都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n現在上層既人玩既係努力收割<br />\n即係<br />\n一味叫你努力多D<br />\n等你做到咁上下,就一句命令/一句說話收割哂所有你既努力<br />\n你多年既努力咁就化為污有<br />\n而佢地就可以hea住肚滿腸肥<br />\n<br />\n你同班賊講努力,笑<br />\n<br />\n搞革命,基本上係反台<br />\n係一種要強烈既行動去推翻呢套<br />\n損失大,動盪係好正常<br />\n<br />\n就好似一個重病病人咁<br />\n你同佢做手術,肯定會有一段時間既陣痛期<br />\n之後就會慢慢好"},{"pid":"c4927b163cc72d5f6338639cd0dd11c5b801d64d","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a47256d78c8aa60b9f9335d08265260c5a132555","tid":1423112,"uid":258258,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"totally agree <br />\n成日講咩環境唔變就人變<br />\n係要奴隸化<br />\n又鐘意blame the victim 真心on 9<br />\n試下去法國講呢D on 9 野實笑死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"叫你努力D=即係想問你搶多D"},{"pid":"67baad8b13e43ea20de010f9afe44cfa18a03b67","tid":1423112,"uid":199523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"招降?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484e10468adac54762a7fef688430b29a566842e","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67baad8b13e43ea20de010f9afe44cfa18a03b67","tid":1423112,"uid":199523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"招降?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6d553c8bb4273c5e436b3e0aceac45d34d89b1","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67baad8b13e43ea20de010f9afe44cfa18a03b67","tid":1423112,"uid":199523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"招降?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"單純批評呢個種族姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42926f2c9daa8797daa2fc768bef3b6ca3883275","tid":1423112,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":1,"sc